## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringmapentry">StringMapEntry</a> - This is used to represent one value that is inserted into a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/stringmap">StringMap</a>.

It contains the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/value">Value</a> itself and the key: the string length and data.

Definition at line 102 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/stringmapentry-h">StringMapEntry.h</a>.
